com.smartsheet.api.models

Class RowWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smartsheet.api.models.RowWrapper

  • public class RowWrapper
extends Object
    Represents the RowWrapper object that is used to specify the location for a Row or set of Rows.
